            üé° Œ°œåŒ¥Œ± ŒîœÅŒ±œÉœÑŒ∑œÅŒπŒøœÑŒÆœÑœâŒΩ
          </h1>
        </div>
      </header>
      
      <main className="p-8">
        <div className="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          {/* Instructions */}
          <div className="text-center mb-10">
